	(text "TODO\n* SPI?\n* UART?\n* SWD? (you can openocd on the pi and reprogram it on the fly? heh)\n* Let's say a UART _at least_ ?\n\nIf you do this \"right\", you can stack it with my of my ADC hats and get a \"HWS2\"\nwithout putting any analog on this board at all...\n\n==> Doesn't even have to stack, can just have the XMC as the \"base\" with a pi adc on top?"
